description:
Today on The Breakfast Club Angela Yee reports on the latest lyric changes in Beyonce's new album. Chance The Rapper also stops by to discuss new music and his ventures in art. Charlamagne gives us todays Donkey Of The Day and positive note (8-2-2022)
